The raw data used for the statistics summary are time series from the COVID-19 Data Repository by the Center for Systems Science and Engineering (CSSE) at Johns Hopkins University. 

The world borders dataset used for the map is from 
https://thematicmapping.org/downloads/world_borders.php	
